Scott Bright was Co-Founder (2002) and former CEO (2009-2012) of Synapse Product Development. Mr. Bright continues to advise and mentor students and new entrepreneurs whenever possible, leveraging his experience as a member of the Advisory Board to the University of Washington (Bothell) School of Business (uwb.edu/business) and the Advisory Board for Washington First Robotics (firstwa.org)

Mr. Bright holds multiple technology patents and received his B.S. in Electrical & Computer Engineering from Ohio University cum laude in 1990 and MBA from the University of Washington, Bothell in 2001.
